description: I used to cross country ski when I was a kid. I had forgotten much since then but that didn´t stop me to have a trip at a ski track. I was looking for young winter athletes today. At the track I met Jakub. He was trying his skis to find out if they´re good for the new season. He wanted to stay fit even during winter. When I talked to him I noticed he was a bit stressed out and tired.  I could tell he was troubled because of his girlfriend. I think she was taking advantage of this sweet boy. He had to work hard to take care of both of them. She didn´t even have a job, what a typical woman. I offered him my help. He had to go with me and earn all the cash he wanted. And he wanted a lot. I´m not sure if the boy had ever tried so many positions during one afternoon.
title: Czech Hunter 285
